244
00:15:27,199 --> 00:15:28,427
Who's the bobblehead of?

245
00:15:29,040 --> 00:15:30,678
Does it matter?

246
00:15:30,879 --> 00:15:32,597
No, as long as it bobbles.

247
00:15:34,959 --> 00:15:36,870
Howie, I am so proud of you.

248
00:15:37,040 --> 00:15:40,271
