267
00:16:38,560 --> 00:16:44,556
So today's first pitch
will be delivered to home plate by science.

268
00:16:44,759 --> 00:16:48,354
Ladies and gentlemen,
boys and girls, I present to you...

269
00:16:48,520 --> 00:16:52,638
