270
00:16:52,800 --> 00:16:53,789
[CROWD CLAPPING]

271
00:16:53,960 --> 00:16:55,188
LEONARD: Whoa!
RAJ ESH: Wow!

272
00:16:56,120 --> 00:16:57,189
Whoo!

273
00:16:58,319 --> 00:17:02,312
